data.description: Home has NEW AC UNIT, NEW STOVE AND MICROWAVE AND A NEW GARAGE DOOR  Welcome to single-story serenity! This beautiful 3-bed, 2-bath home boasts a thoughtfully designed split floorplan, ensuring tranquil privacy with the master suite on one side and two bedrooms on the other. Step into relaxation in the backyard oasis, complete with a patio perfect for entertaining and a sparkling pool to soak away the day's stress. This meticulously maintained home is the epitome of comfort and charm, offering a seamless blend of functionality and style.
